    <text>
        <body>
            <pb facs="MSIAsheet20r"/>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><space quantity="16" unit="chars" /><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="print" medium="ink"/><hi rend="italic"><hi rend="caps">calais</hi></hi></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l><add place="margin-left" rend="counterclockwise">133.0<lb/>110,10</add><handShift new="#HANDJJR" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>The sands are in the sunlight sleeping<add place="margin-right" rend="counterclockwise">1480<lb/>123. 4.</add></l>
                    <l>The ocean Barrier is beating<ref type="gloss_textual" target="calais_poem_glosses_textual.php#CALAISPOEMLINE2"/></l>
                    <l>Again again forevermore</l>
                    <l>Haste the light curlings to the Shore</l>
                    <l><del rend="underline">And yet advance &#x0026; yet retreat</del><add place="above"><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>That from the sand the impression sweep</add><add rend="linenumber-right-JR">5</add></l>
                    <l><handShift script="cursive" medium="ink" corresp="#HANDJJR"/>O<subst><del>n</del><add rend="overwriting"><handShift script="cursive" medium="ink" corresp="#HANDJR1833-34"/>f</add></subst><handShift script="cursive" medium="ink" corresp="#HANDJJR"/> playful childhoods daring feet</l>
                    <l>That seeks within its sandy cell</l>
                    <l>The pebble bright or purple shell<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="calais_glosses_contextual.php#CALAISPOEMSHELL"/></l>
                    <l>Far in its<!-- DCH: I think we can ignore this overwritten i as it's not convincingly a correction --> clear expanse l<subst><del>ies</del><add rend="overwriting"><handShift script="cursive" medium="ink" corresp="#HANDJR1833-34"/>ay</add></subst> wide</l>
                    <l>Unruffledly that ocean tide<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">10</add></l>
                    <l>Stretching away where paler grew</l>
                    <l>The Heavens bright unclouded blue</l>
                    <l>And far away in distance dying</l>
                    <l>Old Englands <damage agent="stain"><unclear resp="DCH">C</unclear></damage>liffy coast is lying</l>
                    <l>And beautiful as summer cloud<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">15</add></l>
                    <l>By the low sun empurpled proud</l>
                    <l>Strange that a space from shore <lb type="runover" rend="below"/><space quantity="31" unit="chars"/>to shore</l>
                    <l>So soon so easily passed oer</l>
                    <l>Should yet a wide distinction place</l>
                    <l>Twixt Man &#x0026; Man twixt Race &#x0026; <lb type="runover" rend="below"/><space quantity="28" unit="chars"/>Race<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">20</add></l>
                    <l>Sudden &#x0026; marked the change you find</l>
                    <l>Religion Language even mind<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="calais_glosses_contextual.php#CALAISPOEMDISTINCTION"/></l>
                    <l>That you might think that oceans <lb type="runover" rend="below"/><space quantity="25" unit="chars"/>span</l>
                    <l>Marked the varieties of Man</l>
                    <!--There is a code at the bottom of this page, apparently unrelated to the work. -->
                </lg>
            </div>
